This talk is always available

00:33:57.636 --> 00:33:58.986
with this link, and make sure to

00:33:58.986 --> 00:34:00.496
check out these sessions too.

00:34:00.496 --> 00:34:01.396
There are some really good ones

00:34:01.456 --> 00:34:03.066
tomorrow on design as well.

00:34:04.936 --> 00:34:06.016
We wish you the best of luck in

00:34:06.016 --> 00:34:07.296
bringing your apps to Apple's

00:34:07.296 --> 00:34:07.946
ecosystem.

